OL,6,FWatch: Dangerous driver continues to
OL,7,Fswerve through traffic with flat tyre
OL,8,Fto flee police
OL,10,FFootage has been released of a driver
OL,11,Fspeeding through traffic with a flat
OL,12,Ftyre as he tried to flee from police
OL,13,Fin Oxfordshire.
OL,15,FOn 4 April, officers tried to stop the
OL,16,Fblack Jeep Cherokee that Adam Marmont
OL,17,Fwas driving near Kidlington.
OL,19,FThey used a stop stick to deflate a
OL,20,Ffront tyre but the 27-year-old
OL,21,Fcontinued to swerve through traffic.
