OL,6,FMarmont sped through Yarnton, Bladon,
OL,7,FEynsham and Stanton Harcourt, at high
OL,8,Fspeeds, doing dangerous overtakes and
OL,9,Fdriving the wrong way round
OL,10,Froundabouts.
OL,12,FDashcam footage shows the front
OL,13,Fnearside tyre was shredding as he
OL,14,Ftried to evade capture.
OL,16,FHis jeep eventually came to a stop
OL,17,Fwhen it collided with the rear of
OL,18,Fanother vehicle on a single track road
OL,19,Fnear Northmoor, before crashing onto a
OL,20,Fgrass verge.
