OL,6,F"It was clear to see the defendant was
OL,7,Fwilling to take needless risks and in
OL,8,Fdoing so put other road users at risk
OL,9,Fof serious harm.
OL,11,F"We will not tolerate behaviour such
OL,12,Fas this on our roads, and will
OL,13,Frobustly pursue and prosecute those
OL,14,Fwho feel it's acceptable to disregard
OL,15,Fthe law."
